<item>
            <title>[LU-10183] If node provisioning fails, Maloo should try again</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10183</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If maloo fails the node-provisioning task, as a user I need to push a new version of the patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be nice if Maloo simply tried again later, or let me press a button to re-run the test, rather than update the patch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="49065">LU-10183</key>
            <summary>If node provisioning fails, Maloo should try again</summary>
